Rails application which integrates with VIVO to provide:

* OAuth-provider functionality to enable external authentication from another app
* Basic wrappers for bibliographic search & lookup via CrossRef


The VIVO installation gains the following main RESTful API endpoints:

# Bibliographic search & retrieval

/railsext/biblio/search Wrapper around CrossRef's SIGG bibliographic search at http://crossref.org/sigg/sigg/FindWorks
/railsext/biblio/fetch  Wrapper around the DOI metadata service at http://dx.doi.org


# OAuth2 provider

/railsext/oauth/authorize
/railsext/oauth/token
/railsext/oauth/revoke
/railsext/oauth/account Retrieve user account info as JSON via access token


